	* forms/form_copyright.fd:
	* forms/form_error.fd:
	* forms/form_tabular.fd:
	* forms/form_toc.fd:
	Consistent shortcuts for Close button: Esc and Return only.

	* forms/form_citation.fd:
	* forms/form_document.fd:
	* forms/form_index.fd:
